OL,7,FAn appeal has been made for witnesses
OL,8,Fto the fatal shooting of a teenager in
OL,9,Fthe grounds of a Belfast hospital
OL,10,Falmost 50 years ago.JPatrick Crawford,
OL,11,F15, was struck by a bullet while
OL,12,Fwalking through the grounds of the
OL,13,FRoyal Victoria Hospital at around
OL,14,F9.40pm on August 10 1975.JA fresh
OL,15,Finquest into his death is examining
OL,16,Fthe circumstances of what happened in
OL,17,Fthe incident, which involved soldiers.
