OL,7,FIt came at a turbulent time in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland on the anniversary of
OL,9,Fthe introduction of internment without
OL,10,Ftrial in 1971.JNurses rushed to the
OL,11,Fteenager's aid, but he died of his
OL,12,Finjuries in A&E.JTwo women, who were
OL,13,Fwalking with him at the time of the
OL,14,Ffatal shooting, gave evidence at the
OL,15,Foriginal inquest in December 1979 that
OL,16,Fthe teenager was unarmed and had asked
OL,17,Fto accompany them from the Grosvenor
OL,18,FRoad to the Falls Road through the
OL,19,Fgrounds of the Royal because he was
OL,20,Fafraid.JPatrick's family believe he
OL,21,Fwas shot dead by the Army in the
OL,22,Fgrounds of the hospital with one high-
OL,23,Fvelocity shot.JA fresh inquest into
OL,24,Fhis death started hearings on March 11
OL,25,Fat Armagh court house, and is set to
OL,26,Fresume on April 8.JUnder the
